  ('dietitian-moex-07064', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-103-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者是負責傳遞痛覺的神經傳遞介質？ 多巴胺  腎上腺素  P物質  血清胺', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:45+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "387d240e6a2b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3812a09b1c9a", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103100", "c": "106", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技醫師中醫師分階段、中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師、法醫師語言聽力牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-07065', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-103-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '正常人在直立的情況下，體循環動脈氧分壓略低於肺泡氧分壓之主因，下列敘述何者正確？ 單位肺體積的通氣量 （ventilation） 由肺尖至肺底呈遞減分布 單位肺體積的灌流 （perfusion） 由肺尖至肺底呈遞減分布 肺底的通氣／灌流比值 （ventilation/perfusion ratio） 遠高於在肺尖之比值 通氣／灌流比值不相稱（mismatch）', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:45+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "387d240e6a2b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3812a09b1c9a", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103100", "c": "106", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技醫師中醫師分階段、中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師、法醫師語言聽力牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-07066', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-103-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關排卵前期激素的變化，下列敘述何者錯誤？ 下視丘促性腺激素釋放激素（GnRH）分泌由低轉高 動情素分泌在排卵前達到高峰 濾泡刺激素（FSH）激增是造成排卵的最重要原因 動情素對黃體刺激素（LH）分泌的調控由負回饋轉為正回饋', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:45+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "387d240e6a2b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3812a09b1c9a", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103100", "c": "106", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技醫師中醫師分階段、中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師、法醫師語言聽力牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-07067', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-103-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '尿毒症的病人最可能會出現下列何種臨床症狀？ 尿糖減少  尿蛋白減少  血鉀降低  紅血球降低', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:45+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "387d240e6a2b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3812a09b1c9a", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103100", "c": "106", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技醫師中醫師分階段、中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師、法醫師語言聽力牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
